entries.npc_1: Shady work here on Naboo if you want it.
entries.npc_2: Well, not everything we do here is strictly above the bar.  Say, you're not with law enforcement are you?
entries.npc_6: Well, then perhaps you could check with some of my associates.  They might have some work for you.
entries.npc_7: Oh.  Well then ignore everything I say.
entries.npc_3: Yes.  Work.  You do know what work is, right?
entries.npc_4: So you're just here on vacation?
entries.npc_8: Ah.  How much money do you have?  Never mind.  I'll find out soon enough...
entries.player_8: No.  I just don't like working.
entries.npc_9: Maybe I should get into your line of "work" then.
entries.npc_5: I could make your business my business...
entries.player_9: Don't bother the pay's too low.
entries.player_10: I don't have money and I don't want a job.
entries.npc_11: Well, you're not doing me much good then are you?
